===1977â78 season===

Important forwards [[Walter Wagner (footballer)|Walter Wagner]] and [[Giorgos Dedes]] both left the club but club chairman [[Loukas Barlos]] replaced them with [[Yugoslavia national football team|Yugoslav]] international [[DuÅ¡an BajeviÄ]] who was one of the best forwards of his time and along with [[Thomas Mavros]] formed one of the most fearsome forward duos in the history of Greek football. BajeviÄ's height and technique perfectly completed Mavros' speed and goalscoring ability.

===Overview===

Under Zlatko Äajkovski AEK Athens played impressive football and achived the domestic double in one of the most successful season in the clubs history.

